OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAirline ads banned over    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'greenwashing' claims      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Adverts for Air France, Lufthansa and  
OL,6, Etihad have been banned for misleading 
OL,7, consumers about the airlines'          
OL,8, environmental impact.                  
OL,10,FAir France's ad said it was "committed 
OL,11,Fto protecting the environment" and     
OL,12,FLufthansa urged passengers to "fly more
OL,13,Fsustainably". Etihad's ad used the     
OL,14,Fwords "environmental advocacy".        
OL,16,FThe Advertising Standards Authority    
OL,17,F(ASA) said the ads did not show the    
OL,18,Fimpact airlines have on climate change.
OL,20,FLufthansa and Etihad removed the ads.  
